Your summoner name isn't showing on here, so I can't look into your specific case.  In general though, PBE and Alpha are separate applications.  Being accepted to the PBE does not also admit a player into testing the alpha client.  Below are the links for each individual sign-up:

[EUW PBE Sign up
](https://pbesignup.euw.leagueoflegends.com/en/pbe)

[EUW Alpha Sign Up
](https://account.leagueoflegends.com/euw/en/alpha)


I hope that helps clear some things up!
